  <brief_title>Relationship Between Tissue Markes in Patients With Post Cardio Respiratory Syndrome</brief_title>
  <official_title>Relationship Between Lactate and Venous Oxygen Saturation Gradient of Carbon Dioxide in Patients With Post Cardio Respiratory Syndrome</official_title>
  <sponsors>
